"The main payment must have a name before a linked payment can be posted."
msgstr ""
"El pago principal debe tener un nombre para que se pueda publicar un pago "
"vinculado."

#. module: l10n_ar_payment_bundle
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/l10n_ar_payment_bundle/models/account_payment.py:0
