"The payment type of the main payment differs from one or more linked "
"payments. Note that the main payment type only impacts withholdings and "
"write-offs."
msgstr ""
"El tipo de pago del pago principal difiere de uno o más pagos vinculados. "
"Tenga en cuenta que el tipo de pago principal solo afecta a las Retenciones "
"y a los Ajustes."

